{"tid":1212721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夏志誠：年輕人走出來只是希望當權者聽到自己意願","createTime":"2019-06-12T21:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T08:19:25.000Z","uid":7790,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2c1bdfef217f97a392346a3f185edda5caa13557","tid":1212721,"uid":7790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T21:16:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462510-20190613.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462510-20190613.htm&d=0lytrcPBTEnksf4YR0ybMUYZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=a1de8d38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1462510-20190613.htm&h=5247bfd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1462510-20190613.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n天主教區輔理主教夏志誠表示，昨晚曾與數十名留守金鐘的青年傾談，形容他們理性、和平、克制，但不知是甚麼原因，亦不知是誰命令，令他們受到暴力對待，為此感到難過。<br />\n<br />\n夏志誠說，或許有人認為這班青年天真，以為多人聚集就會起作用，推遲修訂《逃犯條例》議程，但希望繼續自由生活，生命能受保障，有何過分之處。<br />\n<br />\n夏志誠又說，真正的法律，使人懂得為人著想，甚至犧牲自己。他認為，年輕人走出來，並非為自己，只是站在街上表達意願，希望當權者聽到。"},{"pid":"d1f808254e69f4ad8d54cf7cc2152ed4053fc49a","tid":1212721,"uid":56326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}